flowchart TD
    A[Developer runs: zer0lint check] --> B{Mode?}
    B -- mem0 config --> C[Load ~/.mem0/config.json]
    B -- HTTP mode --> D[Use --add-url / --search-url]

    C --> E[Detect LLM from config]
    D --> F[HTTP adapter]

    E --> G[Inject 5 synthetic facts via mem0.add()]
    F --> G2[POST facts to add endpoint]

    G --> H[Wait for extraction]
    G2 --> H2[Wait http-wait seconds]

    H --> I[Query via mem0.search()]
    H2 --> I2[GET from search endpoint]

    I --> J[Score: facts recalled / total]
    I2 --> J

    J --> K{Score >= 80%?}
    K -- YES --> L[HEALTHY - done]
    K -- NO --> M[Run: zer0lint generate]

    M --> N[Phase 1: Baseline test - current score]
    N --> O[Phase 2: Re-test with zer0lint extraction prompt]
    O --> P{Score improved?}
    P -- YES --> Q[Phase 3: Write prompt to custom_fact_extraction_prompt in config]
    P -- NO --> R[Report: no improvement - manual tuning needed]
    Q --> S[Backup original config with ISO timestamp]
    S --> T[FIXED - restart agent to pick up new prompt]
